<div class="txt-block" id="name-bio-text">
        <div class="name-trivia-bio-text">
                      <div class="inline" itemprop="description">
Michael Winterbottom was born on March 29, 1961 in Blackburn, Lancashire, England. He is a director and producer, known for <a href="/title/tt0274309?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk1">24 Hour Party People</a> (2002), <a href="/title/tt0829459?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk2">A Mighty Heart</a> (2007) and <a href="/title/tt0954947?ref_=nm_ov_bio_lk3">The Killer Inside Me</a> (2010).            <span class="see-more inline nobr-only">
                    <a href="/name/nm0935863/bio?ref_=nm_ov_bio_sm"
>See full bio</a> &raquo;
            </span>
</div>        </div>
</div>

                        
    <div id="name-born-info" class="txt-block">
