    <h2>Did You Know?</h2>
        <div id="dyk-personal-quote" class="see-more inline canwrap">
                <h4 class="inline">Personal Quote:</h4>
When I was at university, the film club always showed In the Realm of the Senses (<a href="/title/tt0074102?ref_=nm_dyk_qt1">In the Realm of the Senses</a> (1976)) at the start of a new year to get people to join. It was full of explicit sex, yet you can buy it in HMV now.                    <span class="see-more inline">
                        <a href="/name/nm0935863/bio?ref_=nm_dyk_qt_sm#quotes"
>See more</a> 
                    </span>
                    &raquo;
        </div>
            <hr/>
        <div id="dyk-trivia" class="see-more inline canwrap">
                <h4 class="inline">Trivia:</h4>
Co-founder of Revolution films (UK); along with producing partner <a href="/name/nm0247787?ref_=nm_dyk_trv1">Andrew Eaton</a>.                    <span class="see-more inline">
                        <a href="/name/nm0935863/bio?ref_=nm_dyk_trv_sm#trivia"
>See more</a>
                    </span>
                    &raquo;
        </div>
    
